{
  "stem": "26983.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then he-- we had to take off all of our clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this letter, which was hidden behind the belt, fell out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- he saw it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- the SS man saw it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took the letter, and he took my number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't punished on the spot at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't hit me at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just took my number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the most frightening and serious thing, because we knew if SS man takes somebody's number, next Sunday-- which was a nonworking day-- I will be called.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so it really happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was called to the Gestapo in Birkenau, which happened to be a block in the beginning of the former Gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was waiting for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, I was very, very afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had enough time to tell the people in the sonderkommando what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told me what I should say and what I should do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they contacted this woman-- because her name was mentioned [INAUDIBLE] in the letter-- how to behave and what to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to say that, well, we were just sweeping and cleaning the compound, and I found the letter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that should have been my excuse, having a letter on me, which was most dangerous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what actually happened, I was sitting hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my friends, who were in this laufers'-- in this compound-- quieted me and tell me, don't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything will be fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was staying on, sitting outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of Germans and a great movement of prisoners-- more or less in the mannerlager, I mean, from where I came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Happened.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
